                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="chat-message-left mb-4">
                                <div>
                                    <img src="~/images/default_avatar.jpg" class="rounded-circle mr-1" width="40" height="40">
                                    <div class="text-muted small text-nowrap mt-2">16:21</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-light rounded py-2 px-3 ml-3">
                                    <div class="font-weight-bold mb-1">Anonim 2</div>
                                    Cras risus ex, imperdiet id augue non, fermentum tempor odio. Nullam consectetur, mi non imperdiet luctus, libero libero ultricies lacus.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="chat-message-left mb-4">
                                <div>
                                    <img src="~/images/default_avatar.jpg" class="rounded-circle mr-1" width="40" height="40">
                                    <div class="text-muted small text-nowrap mt-2">16:22</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-light rounded py-2 px-3 ml-3">
                                    <div class="font-weight-bold mb-1">Anonim 1</div>
                                    Cras risus ex, imperdiet id augue non, fermentum tempor odio. Nullam consectetur, mi non imperdiet luctus, libero libero ultricies lacus.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="chat-message-left mb-4">
                                <div>
                                    <img src="~/images/default_avatar.jpg" class="rounded-circle mr-1" width="40" height="40">
                                    <div class="text-muted small text-nowrap mt-2">16:22</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-light rounded py-2 px-3 ml-3">
                                    <div class="font-weight-bold mb-1">Anonim 2</div>
                                    Cras risus ex, imperdiet id augue non, fermentum tempor odio. Nullam consectetur, mi non imperdiet luctus, libero libero ultricies lacus.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="chat-message-left mb-4">
                                <div>
                                    <img src="~/images/default_avatar.jpg" class="rounded-circle mr-1" width="40" height="40">
                                    <div class="text-muted small text-nowrap mt-2">16:23</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-light rounded py-2 px-3 ml-3">
                                    <div class="font-weight-bold mb-1">Anonim 2</div>
                                    Cras risus ex, imperdiet id augue non, fermentum tempor odio. Nullam consectetur, mi non imperdiet luctus, libero libero ultricies lacus.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="py-3 px-4 border-top">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <textarea rows="3" class="form-control message-area" placeholder="Сообщение"></textarea>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary ml-2 send-button">Отправить</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane" id="profile" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="profile-tab">Товары</div>
                <div class="tab-pane" id="messages" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="messages-tab">Корзина</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    $(function () {
        $('#myTab li:last-child a').tab('show')
    })
</script>

